VQEC_EVENT_SLOW_CHANNEL_CHANGE  Proceed with rapid channel change.
VQEC_EVENT_NAT_BINDING_COMPLETE  NAT binding is complete.

VQEC_EVENT_RECEIVE_INVALID_APP  Received invalid APP packet.

VQEC_EVENT_RCC_IPC_ERR  Error in IPC layer.
VQEC_EVENT_RCC_INTERNAL_ERR  Internal resource allocation error.
VQEC_EVENT_CHAN_DEINIT  Channel deinit event
VQEC_EVENT_NUM_VAL  Must be last.

enum vqec_sm_state_

Enumerator:
VQEC_SM_STATE_INVALID  Invalid state.
VQEC_SM_STATE_INIT  Initial state.
VQEC_SM_STATE_WAIT_APP  In wait for a NAT binding update and APP.
VQEC_SM_STATE_FIN_SUCCESS  Final state: control-plane state machine has terminated.
VQEC_SM_STATE_ABORT  Final state: The operation did not complete successfully, and was aborted.
VQEC_SM_STATE_NUM_VAL  Must be last
